INSERT INTO fanbox_posts (
                    id,
                    creator_id,
                    title,
                    body,
                    is_body_rich,
                    fee,
                    published_datetime,
                    updated_datetime,
                    fetched_at
                ) VALUES (
                    ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, datetime(?, 'utc'), datetime(?, 'utc'), datetime('now', 'utc')
                )
